<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ب ر ر<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٥٤٦ - ب ر ر]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>برَّ٢ بَرِرْتُ، يَبَرّ، ابْرَرْ/ بَرَّ، بِرًّا، فهو بَارّ وبَرّ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• بَرَّ الشَّخصُ:</span> صلَح، ضدّ فجَر.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• برَّ حَجُّه ونحوه:</span> قُبِلَ <span class="c1">"برَّتِ الصَّلاةُ"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• برَّتِ اليمينُ:</span> صَدَقَت.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">• برَّتِ السِّلعةُ:</span> راجتْ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">• برَّ البيعُ:</span> خَلا من الشّبهة والكذب والخيانة.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>